Detailed Description

cvmx_sriomaint::_sec_dev_ctrl

This register enables the secondary 8 and 16 bit device IDs used for large and small transport. The corresponding secondary ID must be written before the ID is enabled. The secondary IDs should not be enabled if the values of the primary and secondary IDs are identical.
